com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.tools
Class MyLog

java.lang.Object
  Application
      com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.tools.MyLog

public class MyLog
extends Application

A custom version of the Log class. By using this for every log statement we are capable of removing all log statements from public view by changing a single line from within string.xml.

These logs are also saved to file using a BufferedWriter and sent to the server during the next SCout campaign request by the saveLog function.
